snippet.title: 🥤Captain Soda - DEMO AVAILABLE NOW! 🥤
snippet.description:
The demo has concluded for this time, thank you to those who played and left feedback, this game wouldn't be possible without you. 

If you are still interested, please wishlist on steam or sign up to the mailing list for updates!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1862950/Captain_Soda/ 
Mailing list: https://colebeernaerts.com/captainsoda

In Captain Soda, you defend Earth against waves of invading aliens using the power of soft drinks.
